<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.10.0">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2026-03-26T18:28:37-07:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Zero Chinese</title><subtitle>From zero Chinese skill to maybe one Chinese skill.</subtitle><entry xml:lang="zh-Hant"><title type="html">Unit 2: 謝謝你</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/26/hsk1-unit2.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Unit 2: 謝謝你" /><published>2026-03-26T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-03-26T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/26/hsk1-unit2</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/26/hsk1-unit2.html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="課文">課文</h2>

<p>A： <mark>謝謝</mark>！<br />
B： <mark>不</mark>謝！</p>

<hr />

<p>A： 謝謝你！<br />
B： <mark>不客氣</mark>！</p>

<hr />

<p>A： <mark>再見</mark>！<br />
B： 再見！</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>New words</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li>謝謝</li>
    <li>不</li>
    <li>不客氣</li>
    <li>再見</li>
  </ol>
</blockquote>

<p>–咖啡❤️</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="HSK1" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[課文]]></summary></entry><entry xml:lang="zh-Hant"><title type="html">Unit 1: 你好</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/24/hsk1-unit1.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Unit 1: 你好" /><published>2026-03-24T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-03-24T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/24/hsk1-unit1</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/24/hsk1-unit1.html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="課文">課文</h2>

<p>A： <mark>你好</mark>！ <br />
B： 你好！</p>

<hr />

<p>A： <mark>您</mark>好！<br />
B： <mark>你們</mark>好！</p>

<hr />

<p>A： <mark>對不起</mark>！ <br />
B： <mark>沒關係</mark>！</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>New words</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li>你</li>
    <li>你們</li>
    <li>您</li>
    <li>對不起</li>
    <li>沒關係</li>
  </ol>
</blockquote>

<p>–咖啡❤️</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="HSK1" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[課文]]></summary></entry><entry xml:lang="zh-Hant"><title type="html">Day Zero</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/23/day-zero.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Day Zero" /><published>2026-03-23T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-03-23T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/23/day-zero</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/zerochinese/2026/03/23/day-zero.html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="你們好">你們好。</h1>

<p>你好，我的名字是 KAT… 我叫 “咖啡” ☕️。</p>

<p>我是學生。<br />
我是音樂老師 （music 老師）。<br />
我不是美國人。 我是加拿大人🇨🇦。</p>

<p>謝謝， 再見。</p>

<p>–咖啡❤️</p>

<p><img src="/zerochinese/assets/images/coffee.jpg" alt="喝咖啡" /></p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="HSK1" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[你們好。]]></summary></entry></feed>